unparalleled combination

offline editing <-> group synchronization <-> community access

completely free of charge without functional restrictions,
but some functions are limited to a number of items in the free version

detailed description at https://inventory.sebag.de


any number of products, stock items, storage locations and shopping lists

optional own product images (pro version)

free configurability also 2-stage :
* Categories
* shopping lists
* Storage locations
* Places of purchase

Input Facilitation :
* Selection of abbreviations (articles etc.)
* Selection from menus (categories etc.)
* Speech input of all texts and numbers
* Voice input also when searching

facilitating automatisms :
* Minimum stock monitoring (Pro version)
* automatic shopping list filling (Pro version)
* Transfer shopping list -> storage location
* Transfer storage location -> other storage location
* Transfer shopping list -> other shopping list
* Takeover product -> Shopping list

Storage of data :
* offline processing
* automatic synchronization
* any number of mobile phones synchronous
* automatic data backup

Special features :
* no login required
* full functionality even without internet connection
* Community extensibility of known products
* Shelf life expiration date Monitoring
* Search options according to selectable criteria.
* 2-step help function everywhere.
* Simultaneous change possibility for several persons in 1 shopping list
* Transfer from shopping list to warehouse
* Transfer from shopping list to consumption statistics
* Recovery of accidentally deleted shopping lists
* automatic and manual sorting
* Several separate warehouse management systems possible

Advantages of the Pro Version per inApp purchase :
* turns advertising off
* Participation in several independent groups
* Participation in groups with more than 2 members
* any number of barcodes
* any number of (synchronized) own product images
* Minimum stock monitoring for any number of products
* CSV-Import / Export unreduced
